Odaily Planet Daily News According to Arkham monitoring data, Grayscale transferred a total of 25,353 ETH to the Coinbase Prime address, including: 
1. Grayscale Ethereum Mini Trust Fund transferred 2,826 ETH to Coinbase Prime Deposit, worth $42.83 million; 
2. Grayscale Ethereum ETF transferred 22,527 ETH to Coinbase Prime hot wallet, worth $5.37 million.
